-- Mol Pares Quarterly Slide as Commodities Rally on EU Meeting
-- B y   A n d r a s   G e r g e l y
-- 2012-06-29T09:16:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-29/mol-pares-quarterly-slide-as-commodities-rally-on-eu-meeting.html
Mol Nyrt. (MOL)  advanced, parings its
slide in the second quarter, as commodities surged on bets
European leaders will contain the debt crisis.  The shares rose 2.5 percent to 16,085 forint by 10:50 a.m.
in Budapest. The stock dropped 13 percent in the second quarter
and 7.4 percent in the first half of 2012.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andras Gergely in Budapest at 
 agergely@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
